{"title":"Save The Rim Brake! BlackHeart Bike Co Releases Road Ti-r, a Road Rocket without Disc Brakes","link":"https://bikerumor.com/blackheart-bike-co-road-ti-r-rim-brake/","date":1719578880000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-Dura-Ace-hero.jpeg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photos/BlackHeart Bike Co.)\" /></p>\n<p>“Do you make rim brake bikes?” BlackHeart Bike Co says they get this question from potential customers “at least once weekly”. And until today, the answer has always been “Sorry, no…”. So, allow me to introduce the new rim brake-equipped <a href=\"https://blackheartbikeco.com/products/road-ti-r\" target=\"_blank\">BlackHeart Bike Co Road Ti-r</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is essentially the same bike as the super popular, award-winning Road Ti that <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/blackheart-bike-co-new-titanium-road/\" target=\"_blank\">we touched on</a> last year, but has been adapted for rim brakes, hence the lil’ “r” on the end there. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-ENVE-rim-brake-fork-e1719505512133.jpeg\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"1094\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-ENVE-rim-brake-fork-e1719505512133.jpeg\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co Road Ti-r ENVE rim brake fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-ENVE-rim-brake-fork-e1719505512133.jpeg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-ENVE-rim-brake-fork-e1719505512133-281x300.jpeg 281w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-ENVE-rim-brake-fork-e1719505512133-112x120.jpeg 112w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-ENVE-rim-brake-fork-e1719505512133-768x821.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/BlackHeart Bike Co.)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Road Ti-r features a modern, aero design paired with an ENVE rim brake fork. The bike is up for pre-order until July 31st. Deliveries are expected in March of 2025. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-rear-tiangle.jpeg\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-rear-tiangle.jpeg\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co Road Ti-r rear tiangle\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-rear-tiangle.jpeg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-rear-tiangle-240x300.jpeg 240w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-rear-tiangle-96x120.jpeg 96w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-rear-tiangle-768x960.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>BlackHeart says that they <em>do</em> need a “minimum order to trigger production”. So, all of you rim brake lovers tell your rim brake loving friends and get your very own Road Ti-r ordered today.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>BlackHeart Road Ti &amp; Road Ti-r Geo and Retail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $1000 (deposit)<br />Frameset: $2149<br />Blackheart Bar &amp; Stem: $2449<br />Zipp Bar &amp; Stem: $2599<br />ENVE Bar &amp; Stem: $2849<br /><strong>Build Kits:</strong><br />SRAM Red AXS D1: $6399<br />Shimano Dura Ace Di2: $6399</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-Zipp-aero-bar-and-stem-e1719505615261.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"819\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-Zipp-aero-bar-and-stem-e1719505615261.jpeg\" alt=\"BlackHeart Bike Co Road Ti-r Zipp aero bar and stem\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/BlackHeart-Bike-Co-Road-Ti-r-Zipp-aero-bar-and-stem-e17195056